edu.harvard.iq.dvn.core.web.study

Class StudyUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.iq.dvn.core.web.study.StudyUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class StudyUI
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Author:
    gdurand Convenience class for Study and StudyVersion information needed in multiple pages. The class does lazy loading of Study and StudyVersion objects. It can be created either with a Study, studyId, StudyVersion or studyVersionId. If a Study or studyId is passed to the constructor, then the StudyVersion is initialized according to the logic in initVersionForStudy()
    See Also:

      • fileMetadataList

        private List<FileMetadata> fileMetadataList
        fileMetadataList is a single list of FileMetadata objects (i.e., not split by file categories). This is created when the StudyUI is going to be used for comparing one study version to another on the Study Differences page.
